title: 151: Adam's Las Vegas Olympia Update
description: Adam is down in Las Vegas for the Olympia, staying in a massive suite at the Palms and doing cool stuff. Sal, Adam & Doug are slaving away in the studio. Adam updates them on the Kai Greene Olympia no-show, but not before making the boys jealous of his playboy lifestyle.
